text: Jeremy Page Rockliff (born 5 February 1970) is a Tasmanian politician. He has served as the Premier of Tasmania and leader of the Tasmanian Liberal Party since 2022 and as one of the five members for Braddon since 2002. He previously served as Deputy Premier from 2014 until 2022. Rockliff is currently the only incumbent Liberal Premier in Australia.
